/* Français — macshot localization
 *
 * To add a new language:
 * 1. Create a new folder: macshot/<lang-code>.lproj/
 * 2. Copy this file into that folder
 * 3. Translate all values (right side of = sign)
 * 4. Add the language to LanguageManager.availableLanguages in Services/LanguageManager.swift
 * 5. Add the language code to knownRegions in macshot.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj
 * 6. Submit a pull request!
 *
 * Keys use the English text. Values should be the translation.
 * Format strings use %@ for strings, %d for integers.
 * Keep keyboard shortcuts (like ⌘C) untranslated.
 * Keep brand names (macshot, Google Drive, imgbb, S3) untranslated.
 */

